Binary Tree to Binary Search Tree Conversion
Given a Binary Tree, convert it to a Binary Search Tree. 
The conversion must be done in such a way that keeps the original structure of Binary Tree.

Examples.

Input:
          100
         /  \
        1    7
       / \
      8   6

Output:
          8
         /  \
        6    100
       / \
      1   7




